- REF

  - http://web.mit.edu/sp.268/www/2010/impartialGames.pdf

- CMD

```
$ k=15;s=0;e=15;seq -s' ' -f "%02g" $s $e|sed 's/^/A1 /'|ag $k;paste -d' ' <(seq -f "%02g" $s $e;) <(for((i=$s;i<=$e;i++));do for((j=$s;j<=$e;j++));do echo $i $j;done;done|opy 'print(str(F1^F2).zfill(2))'|xargs -n$[e+1]) | ag $k
```
